products.description: Get accelerated performance for better gaming and pro-level multitasking with graphics-intensive apps. Powered by 3D NAND technology, the SanDisk Ultra 3D SSD delivers enhanced endurance and reliability, blazing sequential read speeds of up to 560MB/s [550MB/s: 250GB only] and sequential write speeds of up to 530MB/S2 [525MB/s: 250GB only] for no-wait boot-up, shorter application load times, and quicker data transfers). in addition to cooler, quieter computing, the SanDisk Ultra 3D SSD includes proven shock- and vibration-resistance to protect your drive.
